revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}

This template generates an external link from a [[persistent identifier]] for a metadata entry within the [[Japan Center for Asian Historical Records]] (JACAR), a part of the [[National Archives of Japan]].

== Usage ==
Standard usage as a citation is:
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{JACAR|ID|Title}}</syntaxhighlight> or <syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{JACAR|id=ID|title=Title|editor=Editor}}</syntaxhighlight>

To generate only the URL:
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{JACAR|ID|plainurl=1}}</syntaxhighlight> or <syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{JACAR|id=ID|plainurl=1}}</syntaxhighlight>

For compatibility with the Japanese version of this template,
<syntaxhighlight lang="wikitext" inline>{{JACAR|ID|Title|1}}</syntaxhighlight> generates a less verbose link.

The <code>ID</code> is the key for the item found in the URL
<code><nowiki>https://www.jacar.archives.go.jp/aj/meta/MetSearch.cgi?IS_KEY_S1=</nowiki><span style="color:green">ID</span><nowiki>&SUM_KIND=SimpleSummary&IS_KIND=detail&IS_SCH=META&IS_STYLE=...</nowiki></code>

== Examples ==
*<code><nowiki>{{JACAR|A10110299500|plainurl=1}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{JACAR|A10110299500|plainurl=1}}
*<code><nowiki>{{JACAR|A10110299500|故上杉輝虎外四名贈位ノ件|1}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{JACAR|A10110299500|故上杉輝虎外四名贈位ノ件|1}}
*<code><nowiki>{{JACAR|A10110299500|故上杉輝虎外四名贈位ノ件}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{JACAR|A10110299500|故上杉輝虎外四名贈位ノ件}}

== See also ==
*{{tl|NDLPID}}
*{{tl|JPNO}}

== External links ==
* [https://www.jacar.archives.go.jp/aj/meta/reference-en Search by Reference Code] Japan Center for Asian Historical Records (JACAR), National Archives of Japan


